title: Kanda Restaurante Cafe
description: Set menu lunches Ejecutivo for approx $3000 pesos, or Kanda for approx $4000 pesos, both of which include soup, mixed salad, brown rice, beans, fruit juice, and a small dessert. The Kanda lunch comes also with a fake meat entree. Fresh fruit juices, wholegrain cookies available. Many table in a nice open courtyard or a more private large backroom. Relaxing Indian music in background.
